---
---
<section id="about" class="about container">
  <div class="section-header reveal-stagger">
    <div class="section-label">THE STUDIO</div>
    <h2 class="reveal-split">Quietly confident.</h2>
    <h2 class="reveal-split">Secretly feral.</h2>
    <p class="reveal">We believe in building games that feel alive before you even hit start. Digital comfort food laced with neon and adrenaline. We don't just polish; we give it teeth.</p>
    <div class="quote-section reveal">
      <blockquote class="main-quote" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
        "Do it because you can, not because others say you shouldn't."
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about h2 {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 9vw, 52px);
    }

    /* Cards stack naturally because they are not grid yet, but let's be sure */
    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .quote-section {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .main-quote {
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 1.8rem);
    }

    .main-quote::before {
      font-size: 3rem;
      top: -15px;
      left: -5px;
    }

    .main-quote::after {
      font-size: 3rem;
      bottom: -30px;
      right: -5px;
    }
  }

  .about {
    padding-top: clamp(64px, 10vw, 140px);
    padding-bottom: 0; /* Let WhyPlay pick up the rest */
  }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem; /* Tightened gap */
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    color: #444;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .quote-section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .main-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--black);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    position: relative;
  }

  .main-quote::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: -10px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--yellow);
    opacity: 0.3;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }

  .main-quote::after {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -40px;
    right: -10px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--pink);
    opacity: 0.3;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }
</style>
